casebody.data:
W. E. HAMNER, et al., v. FLORIDA LAND HOLDING CORPORATION 22 So. (2nd) 813

June Term, 1945

July 17, 1945 Division B Massari, Patton & Spicola, for W. E. Hamner, J. W. B. Shaw, for E. L. Hamner and Nathan R. Graham and Paul E. Dixon, for et al. intervenors, appellants, Earle B. Askew, for appellee. *313PER CURIAM:

The decree appealed from is affirmed. See Rhode, as executor, etc., v. Gallat, 70 Fla. 536, 70 So. 471; Smith v. Shackleford, 92 Fla. 731, 110 So. 358.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
